@SmartRentApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5184

### WEATHER FORECAST

GET {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

### ---------------- AUTH & USERS ----------------
### Register Admin Account
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Super Admin",
  "email": "admin@smartrent.com",
  "password": "AdminPassword123!",
  "role": 0
}
### 1. Register a Tenant (Auto-Approved)
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": 0
}

### 2. Register a Landlord (Pending)
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Jane Landlord",
  "email": "landlord@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": 1
}

### 2.5 Login to get JWT Token
## save token in variable token 
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "landlord@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### 3. Approve Landlord (Admin)
# Replace {id} with the ID of the landlord created above
## add header authorization with token
PUT {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/admin/landlords/3/approve
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..RYjZtuGnV5W7cBe-3NL23dmsbrh_leJxlKdRJhXZx8M

### ---------------- PROPERTIES ----------------

### 4. Create Property (Requires an Approved Landlord ID)
# Replace landlordId with an approved landlord ID
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..aNJq4kV39a88cg9WSxZdJoqpziss9TDrTw58j3rkF9c

{
  "landlordId": 3,
  "title": "Beautiful Apartment in City Center",
  "description": "A nice and cozy apartment...",
  "price": 1200.50,
  "location": "City Center, Main Street 123",
  "type": 0,
  "hasParking": true,
  "hasElevator": true,
  "isFurnished": true
}

### 5. Approve Property (Admin)
# Replace {id} with the newly created property ID
PUT {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/admin/properties/2/approve
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..RYjZtuGnV5W7cBe-3NL23dmsbrh_leJxlKdRJhXZx8M

### 6. Get All Available Properties
GET {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/properties
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get Available Properties with Filters
GET {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/properties?location=City&minPrice=1000&type=0
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get Property By ID
# Replace {id} with a valid property ID
GET {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/properties/1
Accept: application/json

### ---------------- NEW FEATURES ----------------

### 9. Add Property to Favorites (Tenant)
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <tenant_token_here>

{
  "propertyId": 1
}

### 10. Request a Visit (Tenant)
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/visits
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <tenant_token_here>

{
  "propertyId": 1,
  "scheduledDate": "2026-05-10T10:00:00Z"
}

### 11. Accept Visit Request (Landlord)
PUT {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/visits/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <landlord_token_here>

{
  "status": 1
}

### 12. Submit Rental Application (Tenant)
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <tenant_token_here>

{
  "propertyId": 1,
  "documentUrl": "https://example.com/my-documents.pdf"
}

### 13. Accept Rental Application (Landlord) - Changes Property to Rented!
PUT {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/applications/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <landlord_token_here>

{
  "status": 1
}

### 14. Add Review (Tenant - Must have rented the property)
POST {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <tenant_token_here>

{
  "propertyId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Amazing property, the landlord was great!"
}

### 15. Get Landlord's Own Properties (Landlord)
GET {{SmartRentApi_HostAddress}}/api/properties/my-properties
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <landlord_token_here>
